7127/20150213_hardsoldeerproef_cat_I_rzk1yo.pdf\">Practice test brazing category I</a><ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077135/schema_hardsoldeerproef_cat_i_esqpuj.pdf\">Scheme of practical brazing test category I</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077129/20150213_hardsoldeerproef_cat_II_yvqw3n.pdf\">Brazing test category II</a><ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077136/schema_hardsoldeerproef_cat_ii_juoykp.pdf\">Brazing test schedule brazing practice category II</a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>STEP 2: <a href=\"https://loket-erkenningen-leefmilieu.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/registreer-voor-erkenning-van-rechtswege\">Register for recognition as a refrigeration technician via the self-management counter 'My VLAREL recognition'.</a></strong></p><ul><li>You need to log in with your eID to do this. Without registration, you cannot start working as a refrigeration technician.</li><li>As soon as you have obtained a <strong>European certificate</strong> and you have registered<strong>, </strong>you will receive an <strong>e-mail </strong>with your<strong> recognition number </strong>and further practical information.</li></ul><h3>You already have a European certificate as a refrigeration technician</h3><p><strong>STEP 1: <a href=\"https://loket-erkenningen-leefmilieu.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/registreer-voor-erkenning-van-rechtswege\">register for recognition as a refrigeration technician via the self-management counter 'My VLAREL recognition'.</a></strong></p><p><strong>STEP 2 </strong>: provide a copy of <strong>your European certificate</strong> (e.g. F-gassendiploma from the Netherlands) in Dutch, French, German or English via <strong>a notification of the use of the recognition </strong>in the <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/natuur-milieu-en-klimaat/erkenning-als-technicus-deskundige-opleidingscentrum-of-labo/erkenningenloket-omgeving\">online recogniti